                        <interp inst="t18370612-name-793" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN HUNT</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I got this shilling, and took the pri<lb></lb>soner—nothing was found on him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18370612-name-794" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18370612-name-794" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
