                        <interp inst="t18370612-name-794" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN FIELD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am Inspector of coin to the Mint. This half-crown is counterfeit, and also the 2 shillings—they have been cast in the same mould.</p>
